          <div style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 12px;">Gap #1 — Practice</div>
          <p style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65;">Most candidates prepare in their heads — which is nothing like a real interview. Without simulation, nerves take over. With simulation, you own the room.</p>
