          <div style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 12px;">Gap #3 — Access</div>
          <p style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65;">Premium coaching costs hundreds per session. For most of the world, interview preparation is either unaffordable or unavailable. That changes now.</p>
